column5: I plan on going fishing by my self tomorrow morning on lake Simcoe at five oclock am for what ever is in season and enjoy some solitude. I do how ever have room to take some one with me if some one wanted to get out . I plan to be out six to seven hours before i need to head in .
invitation like this are rare...i applaud you...would love to take you up on this however work and distance wont allow it lots of luck..enjoy the trip
Thank you , you never know one day down the road  .
IN THAT SITUATION RIGHT NOW...BOAT DOWN...AWAY TO OTTAWA FOR WORK..BUT A GOOD FRIEND BIG CLIFF   HAS  HELPED BY GETTING ME OUT FOR THE LITTLE TIME I HAVE AT HOME..IT IS SOOOOO APPRECIATED!!!!!
